==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Abutter
<hw>A*but"ter</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, abuts. Specifically, the owner of a contiguous estate; <as>as,
the <ex>abutters</ex> on a street or a river</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Abuzz</ent>⟦br⟧
